  <brief_title>Is There a Relationship Between Previous Exposure to General Anesthesia and the Development of Alzheimer´s Disease?</brief_title>
  <acronym>DEMA</acronym>
  <official_title>A Case-control Study of Exposure to General Anesthesia and a Diagnosis of Alzheimer´s Disease Later in Life.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
